{"tid":1890842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後中國和中国 要分開嚟講","createTime":"2020-02-21T11:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:51:14.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b0159390da4ab17c5916623c2f7ef5a034050df","tid":1890842,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"台灣人，台灣叫中華民國，人哋先係簡稱台灣又名&quot;中國&quot; 。<br />\n<br />\n強國蝗果啲係中国， 佢哋就算去頭去尾嘅簡稱都只係 &quot;中国&quot;。佢哋自己都唔認自己係中國人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要正視聽唔好俾佢哋污蔑同冒認人哋台灣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫班大中華膠咪話自己係中國人，要寫就寫中国。 講嘅話叫佢哋用蝗語唔該，中国官方聲稱廣東話唔係正統語言。自認中国人請在日常生活使用蝗語(普通話)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人先會識用沿遠流長嘅廣東話嘅，提佢哋要政治正確喎。 睇佢哋班廢佬有幾多個學到正。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣的中文，香港嘅中文 和 中国的中文，連用語都係唔同嘅。叫佢哋唔好用錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我今鋪仲唔係光明正大在連登用蝗字唔會俾人屌嘅人?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749dd35fc8d66a6d652110a548e92db0913d4b64","tid":1890842,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"叫支那冇得錯"},{"pid":"36830924df74c633cd1f7173aa1c73e0a323665d","tid":1890842,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749dd35fc8d66a6d652110a548e92db0913d4b64","tid":1890842,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"叫支那冇得錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"無錯， 自己一直分開叫中國同支那"}]}